      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "DealProposal: signatory seller, observer buyer\nAcceptProposal: controller buyer -> creates TradeFinanceDeal(status = proposed)\nTradeFinanceDeal: signatory seller + buyer, observer regulator\nApproveDeal: controller regulator, requires proposed | SettleDeal: controller buyer, requires approved\nDisputeDeal: controller buyer, allowed before settlement, blocked after settled",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
