      "originalText": "DealProposal: signatory seller, observer buyer\nAcceptProposal: controller buyer -> creates TradeFinanceDeal(status = proposed)\nTradeFinanceDeal: signatory seller + buyer, observer regulator\nApproveDeal: controller regulator, requires proposed | SettleDeal: controller buyer, requires approved\nDisputeDeal: controller buyer, allowed before settlement, blocked after settled",
